{"tid":2038263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtube 戰線：有馬拉Youtuber 散播金融風暴中央救港假新聞","createTime":"2020-05-27T12:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T01:03:25.000Z","uid":64492,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af97f09e52768162b8175600bf1917bde9a0b497","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W9rjjhA1x80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW9rjjhA1x80&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32S%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=0a0dd880\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W9rjjhA1x80</a><br />\n呢條友一直有留意佢，以前講得比較多馬拉輕鬆topic。但今日出咗呢條片，真係嚇鳩死。全香港，甚至全亞洲都知個時中共外匯唔夠，自救都未搞掂，點樣輸出外匯救香港，on9到極致。<br />\n<br />\n我再睇返佢啲片，真心懷疑係中共思想輸出嘅一部分。（為免變相幫佢刷流量，大家睇我description 就得）<br />\n  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0NOTwqH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0NOTwqH.png&h=473b7361&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢條片宣傳中國youtuber<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X59O4LH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX59O4LH.png&h=49d1dde4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條片講印尼排華，但唔單止講印尼華僑返中國幾咁感動，仲唔提及文革時華僑被批鬥嘅慘況。亦暗示係美國搞局，挑起民族仇恨，完全無視印尼共產黨係由中共輸出革命嘅事實。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMkCdD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMkCdD1.png&h=eea536c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫愛抄藝洗白，講到係干預自由市場運作咁。<br />\n<br />\n佢subscriber 唔算多，受眾主要係馬拉華人（好多都係小粉紅）同大陸人，但係又用繁體，好明顯想營造國際華人撐中共嘅image。傳播正確史實，我哋有責任，唔俾中共支線網紅抹黑！！"},{"pid":"aa7386be3abdbb5a2b3211a320c8dae48f428997","tid":2038263,"uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b733172ea8a3a27cdf926759e2926f165dc69aa3","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推，成件事唔係KOL100咁簡單。<br />\n中共要粉飾太平，唔會只係用自己大陸網紅，仲會擴散去到其他華人圈。而家加拿大已經俾大陸人攻佔，香港要係全世界得到支持，就要搶奪華文群體嘅話語權。"},{"pid":"08d3672df509b28154fea3a9c2f23bc4e4ff9766","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b9a5051f0565400718d731d043bc1122b589d81","tid":2038263,"uid":135628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"541b64365f1e240e4bb147d096d53a1c775f652d","tid":2038263,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"又講中央救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬拉狗真係弱撚智"},{"pid":"1d6c7e51f78d5d735e2f760578dddca8c96f3949","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:02:15.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫手推一推"},{"pid":"59b4da515902f8637d96b222c06475b4c1130c1c","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"541b64365f1e240e4bb147d096d53a1c775f652d","tid":2038263,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"又講中央救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬拉狗真係弱撚智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪逼害心理，成日覺得自己俾土著欺凌，幻想中共係一個理想國。"},{"pid":"47eaa4c44f436469dc2c04c12fa55c13ced55c3c","tid":2038263,"uid":64492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply